# textdomain: mcl_boats
Sneak to dismount=潜行以离开
Boats are used to travel on the surface of water.=船用于在水面上航行。
Rightclick on a water source to place the boat. Rightclick the boat to enter it. Use [Left] and [Right] to steer, [Forwards] to speed up and [Backwards] to slow down or move backwards. Use [Sneak] to leave the boat, punch the boat to make it drop as an item.=右键点击水源来放置船，右键点击船进入船内。使用【左】和【右】键操控方向，使用【前】键加速，使用【后】键减速或向后移动。使用【潜行】键离开船，击打船使其变为物品掉落。
Boat=船
Water vehicle=水上运输工具
Chest Boats are used to travel on the surface of water. And transport goods=驶于水上，运输货物
Rightclick on a water source to place the boat. Rightclick the boat to enter it. Use [Left] and [Right] to steer, [Forwards] to speed up and [Backwards] to slow down or move backwards. Use [Sneak] to leave the boat, punch the boat to make it drop as an item. Use [Sneak] + [Rightclick] to open the boat's chest=右键点击水源来放置小船。右键点击小船便可进入其中。使用[向左]和[向右]键来操控方向，使用[向前]键来加速，使用[向后]键来减速或者向后移动。使用[潜行]键离开小船，击打小船可使其掉落成为一个物品。使用[潜行]+[右键点击]来打开小船的储物箱
Chest Boat=运输船
